# Profile Image Placeholder

This file serves as a placeholder for the profile image. 

To use your own profile image:
1. Replace this file with your actual profile image
2. Name it `profile.jpg` or update the src attribute in `index.html`
3. Recommended size: 400x400 pixels
4. Supported formats: JPG, PNG, WebP

For now, the CSS will handle the missing image gracefully with a fallback background.